&lt;li&gt;Working with tools and methods that will keep changing under your feet, and being expected to engage with that change, not wait it out&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bringing judgment to work the platform helps with — applying the right criteria, catching what looks fine but isn&#39;t, knowing when to push back&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
