&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI fluency.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Not enthusiasm, not curiosity — fluency. You should already be using AI in your work and have a real point of view about where it helps and where it shouldn&#39;t.&lt;/li&gt;
